As a powerful 8th class mage, Ian Paige took countless innocent lives under the orders of Emperor Ragnar, a close friend and ruler of the Greenriver Empire. Yet despite their closeness, Ragnar views Ian as a threat and subsequently poisons him. Using time magic, Ian saves himself and returns 30 years to the past. Now a young boy, Ian joins an elite order of mages to hone his abilities once again. This time, hell get revenge on the emperor who betrayed him and reclaim glory as an 8th class mage!
(Source: Tapas)

Woken up from a date, hes suddenly in a movie set? Wait, hes been reborn as a baby martial artist! In the Jongnam Clan, which was once one of the 9 strongest clans, he receives the name Gun-Chung and uses the knowledge of his past life to learn the true meaning of martial arts. When your perspective is different, your martial arts changes. Armed with knowledge, Gun-Chung brings about a new age of martial arts!
